function migrateMission_000001(missionData: any): void {
  for (let nodeDatum of missionData.nodeData as any) {
    let actionsAvailable: number = nodeDatum.executable
      ? nodeDatum.actions.length
      : 0

    nodeDatum.preExecutionText = `${
      nodeDatum.name
    } has ${actionsAvailable} available action${
      actionsAvailable === 1 ? '' : 's'
    }.`

    for (let action of nodeDatum.actions) {
      action.resourceCost = 1
      action.postExecutionSuccessText = `${action.name
        .substring(0, 1)
        .toUpperCase()}${action.name.substring(
        1,
        action.name.length,
      )} was performed successfully on ${nodeDatum.name}.`
      action.postExecutionFailureText = `${action.name
        .substring(0, 1)
        .toUpperCase()}${action.name.substring(
        1,
        action.name.length,
      )} was performed unsuccessfully on ${nodeDatum.name}.`
    }

    delete nodeDatum.postExecutionSuccessText
    delete nodeDatum.postExecutionFailureText
  }
}
